  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits is a relaxing yet strategic tile-based puzzle game where you build cities on a desolate island. Place tiles carefully to trigger cascading expansions and maximize your score. Plan efficiently to cover as much land as possible before space runs out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/4fa6425c33ee70e9b1b9184e6226c109.avif?t=1740634667\" width=560 height=117 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle-based score chasing gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes to mix and match</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Chill songs to build to</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save and quit any run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards to compete against other city planners</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What City Limits Is and is Not</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits <i>is</i> a chill and relaxing experience. It <i>is</i> best played with headphones. It <i>is </i>deeper than it seems.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits <i>is not</i> a super long game. It's <i>not</i> a traditional city builder.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/0eb89d4a3095dcb2b43c64986869ec1a.poster.avif?t=1740634667\" width=762 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/0eb89d4a3095dcb2b43c64986869ec1a.webm?t=1740634667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/0eb89d4a3095dcb2b43c64986869ec1a.mp4?t=1740634667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits is a relaxing yet strategic tile-based puzzle game where you build cities on a desolate island. Place tiles carefully to trigger cascading expansions and maximize your score. Plan efficiently to cover as much land as possible before space runs out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/4fa6425c33ee70e9b1b9184e6226c109.avif?t=1740634667\" width=560 height=117 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle-based score chasing gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes to mix and match</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Chill songs to build to</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save and quit any run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards to compete against other city planners</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What City Limits Is and is Not</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits <i>is</i> a chill and relaxing experience. It <i>is</i> best played with headphones. It <i>is </i>deeper than it seems.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >City Limits <i>is not</i> a super long game. It's <i>not</i> a traditional city builder.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/0eb89d4a3095dcb2b43c64986869ec1a.poster.avif?t=1740634667\" width=762 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056550/extras/0eb89d4a3095dcb2b43c64986869ec1a.webm?t=1740634667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta